OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772129063
OL,3,CPolice raid illegal 'skinny jabs'
OL,4,Cfactory
OL,6,FPolice seized drugs and equipment
OL,7,Fafter raiding an undercover factory
OL,8,Fbeing used to manufacture illegal so-
OL,9,Fcalled "skinny jabs".
OL,11,FOfficers from Lincolnshire Police
OL,12,Fbroke into an agricultural property in
OL,13,FNewton, near Sleaford, on Tuesday, as
OL,14,Fpart of an ongoing investigation into
OL,15,Funregulated weight-loss products
OL,16,Fadvertised on social media.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772129063
OL,3,CPolice raid illegal 'skinny jabs'
OL,4,Cfactory
OL,6,FThey seized thousands of doses of the
OL,7,Fdrug, equipment used in the
OL,8,Fmanufacturing process, vehicles, and a
OL,9,Flarge quantity of pharmaceutical
OL,10,Fingredients.
OL,12,FThe force, which was supported by
OL,13,FTrading Standards and immigration
OL,14,Fenforcement officials, along with the
OL,15,FMedicines and Healthcare Products
OL,16,FRegulatory Agency (MHRA), said it
OL,17,Ffollowed complaints of users becoming
OL,18,Funwell.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772129063
OL,3,CPolice raid illegal 'skinny jabs'
OL,4,Cfactory
OL,6,FA residential address in Grantham was
OL,7,Falso searched but no arrests have yet
OL,8,Fbeen made.
OL,10,FA Lincolnshire Police spokesperson
OL,11,Fsaid: "The seizure represents a major
OL,12,Fdisruption to an organised crime group
OL,13,Fsuspected of producing unlicensed
OL,14,Fweight loss substances and selling
OL,15,Fthem online.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772129063
OL,3,CPolice raid illegal 'skinny jabs'
OL,4,Cfactory
OL,6,F"Investigators believe the products
OL,7,Fwere being marketed online, including
OL,8,Fsocial media platforms such as TikTok,
OL,9,Fenabling rapid and widespread
OL,10,Fdistribution of unregulated and
OL,11,Fpotentially dangerous drugs."
OL,13,FA similar raid was carried out in
OL,14,FNorthamptonshire in October, which led
OL,15,Fto the seizure of weight loss pens,
OL,16,Fraw chemical ingredients, and more
OL,17,Fthan 2,000 unlicensed injection pens,
OL,18,Fworth more than #250,000.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
