OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772129063
OL,3,CPolice raid illegal 'skinny jabs'
OL,4,Cfactory
OL,6,FThe MHRA has warned that illicit
OL,7,Fweightloss injections pose a serious
OL,8,Fand potentially fatal risk.
OL,10,FAndy Morling, head of the MHRA's
OL,11,Fcriminal enforcement unit, said:
OL,12,F"Every illegal product seized, every
OL,13,Farrest, every prosecution brings us
OL,14,Fcloser to dismantling these networks
OL,15,Fcompletely and protecting the public,
OL,16,Fand we will stop at nothing to hold
OL,17,Fcriminals to account for the harm they
OL,18,Fare knowingly doing."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772129063
OL,3,CPolice raid illegal 'skinny jabs'
OL,4,Cfactory
OL,6,FDet Insp Samuel Ward, of Lincolnshire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "The production and sale
OL,8,Fof counterfeit weight loss drugs is
OL,9,Fincredibly dangerous - these
OL,10,Fsubstances are unregulated and pose a
OL,11,Freal risk to anyone who uses them.
OL,13,F"Criminal groups exploiting vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople for profit have no place in our
OL,15,Fcommunities, and we will continue to
OL,16,Fwork relentlessly with our partners to
OL,17,Fdismantle these operations and keep
OL,18,Fthe public safe."
OL,26,@oD@OOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
