OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772129063
OL,3,CPolice raid illegal 'skinny jabs'
OL,4,Cfactory
OL,6,FAndy Wright, from Lincolnshire County
OL,7,FCouncil Trading Standards, added: "The
OL,8,Fpublic must be aware of the
OL,9,Fsignificant health risks associated
OL,10,Fwith these unlicensed substances.
OL,12,F"The product involved remains in
OL,13,Fclinical trials and has not been
OL,14,Fcertified for use in any form ` and
OL,15,Fthat certification is there to protect
OL,16,Fpeople from dangerous, untested
OL,17,Fingredients."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
